      "description": "After warming up, the focus today is on improving your aerobic endurance. The main set consists of a variety of low-intensity aerobic efforts. Relax and enjoy the ride today.\n\nWarmup\n- 10m ramp 45.4-75.4%\n\n- 1m 62.9%\n- 7m 73%\n- 1m 62.9%\n- 6m 68%\n- 1m 62.9%\n- 7m 73.4%\n- 1m 62.9%\n- 6m 68.4%\n- 1m 62.9%\n- 7m 73%\n\nCooldown\n- 10m ramp 75.4-45.4%"
    },
